{"tid":1745144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強：被捕者指控遭警方暴力對待並非新鮮事","createTime":"2019-11-22T05:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:25:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7c68c663ce77a0e281b1d8384f82524030ecea","tid":1745144,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"有報道指早前在理工大學離開的人經警方登記後未能離境，警務處處長鄧炳強澄清是假消息。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強表示，有成年涉案人離開理大時要求送院，送上救護車抵達醫院後卻未有入院，並立即潛逃，因此警方要將涉案人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n對於日前有裁判官稱，被捕者供稱在拘捕及羈留期間遭警方暴力對待的指控嚴重，要求警方跟進，鄧炳強表示，「拉一個人並唔容易」，因為會有反抗，故需要數人制服。有記者表明有影片拍攝警方對被捕者拳打腳踢，質疑是否合理武力，鄧炳強沒直接回應，僅表示一般情況下在完全控制被捕者才能拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強又稱，被捕者指控遭警方暴力對待並非新鮮事，警方會按既定機制處理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2310242/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2310242%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=ea9a9772\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2310242/</a>"},{"pid":"b83eb5e77630b7133a70fcdde336bd3e742cfe35","tid":1745144,"uid":199811,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:31:40.000Z","msg":"呢件鄧炳強講野咁痴線 同佢堆細嘅冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3fff2588c2d89c32788284ded68f7301d8e2a3","tid":1745144,"uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"立左大功<br />\n係唔同d <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過左人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c98ee54b54365de98dd679671a6ea31c3a08a7","tid":1745144,"uid":241979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"幾撚大支野 話比你聽：old news我都知啦<br />\n使撚你地嚟話我知"},{"pid":"ef9015fbf1513a2a64cdb9cfef7ac2be0c83495a","tid":1745144,"uid":50347,"